Target and Connect Intelligently 
		

We intelligently connect you with your audience through real-time data-driven optimization. 
		


 


 

 

 

Our programmatic marketing platform was built by people who are passionate about finding intelligent ways for advertisers to connect with consumers. Since opening our doors in 2009, we’ve grown from a 7 person business to a public company with presence in Toronto, Montreal, New York, Los Angeles, Boston and Portland.  Let our team of Optimization Specialists manage your campaigns from start to finish.  For those who prefer a more hands on approach, ask about our self-serve solution that allows you to bring your programmatic buying in-house.

Real Time Data OptimizationOur industry leading refresh rate allows for smarter targeting decisions, less fraudulent impressions and better cost efficiencies. 
Brand Safety TechnologyWe offer a multi-layer approach to brand safety so that your ad does not appear within unsafe brand environments.
Screen Agnostic PlatformOur User Interface enables real-time buying and optimization across display, video, mobile and social – all within one reporting platform.

Want To Know What Canadian Marketers Think About Programmatic Advertising?We partnered with Marketing Magazine and Rogers Research for the first Canadian Programmatic Landscape Study!



 
 
 


 

